>> source: https://cakedecorist.com/how-to-sweeten-coconut-flakes/
>> total time: 15 minutes

In a #small saucepan{}, heat the @water{1/4%cup} and @granulated sugar{4%tsp} together with the heat set to medium.

Add the @unsweetened coconut flakes{1%cup} to the water and sugar mixture. Stir the mixture with the coconut until the water is absorbed. Once the water is absorbed, remove the coconut from the heat.

Add the coconut to your #baking sheet{} lined with #parchment paper{} and let it dry.
